snippet.title: PsiloSybil Announcement Trailer - old school 3d platforming!
snippet.description:
Steam Page (includes demo): https://store.steampowered.com/app/1696720/PsiloSybil/?l=english



Demo (from itch): https://cancrizans.itch.io/psilosybil-demo


Support development on Patreon (and get access to the alpha): https://www.patreon.com/bad_vertex


PsiloSybil is inching towards early access beta! It's my passion project, more than a love letter to Crash Bandicoot and the 32-bit era. It's a really challenging game that I hope brings you a lot of fun.


Coming to PC only. It supports most gamepads natively.


Join the PsiloSybil Discord server! We don't bite. https://discord.gg/rgjZJPs
